          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Lobbying Disclosure Improvement Act&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires registered lobbyists to disclose whether they are exempt from having to register as foreign agents due to their lobbying activities and status as registered lobbyists.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
